  "dct_description_sm": [
    "Bolivia Social Census Data, 2012 is a polygon theme representing Municipios (3rd level administrative units) in Bolivia as of 2012. Attribute data include summary results of the 2012 Bolivian census questions regarding language, education, healthcare, children and other social characteristics. The documentation of these variables can be found in the \"Social\" section from the accompanying code book. This dataset is part of Bolivia 2012 Census collection."
